docs {
  # Scan Image

  Scans an image URL using OCR to extract text.

  ## Request Body
  - `url`: URL of the image to scan

  ## Response
  Returns extracted text from the image as an array of lines.
  
  ## Supported Languages
  - English (en, en-GB)
  - Dutch (nl, nl-BE)
}

